description.p:
The present disclosure provides a compound of formula I
wherein
Ra is H; C1-4alkyl; or C1-4alkyl substituted by OH, NH2, NHC1-4alkyl or N(C1-4alkyl)2;
Rb is H; halogen; C1-8alkyl; or C1-8alkoxy, and
R is a radical of formula (a)
wherein each of R1 and R2, independently, is H or methyl;
R3 is F, Cl, acetamide, nitro or amino;
R4 is H, CH3, CF3, F, or Cl; R4 being other than H, CH3 or CF3 when R3 is Cl.

In accordance with the foregoing the present invention further provides:
1.1 Compounds for use in a method for preventing or treating disorders or diseases mediated by T lymphocytes and/or PKC or G SK-3β, e.g. such as indicated a bove, in a subject in need of such treatment, which method comprises administering to said subject an effective amount of a compound of formula I or a pharmaceutically acceptable salt thereof;
1.2 Compounds for use in a method for preventing or treating acute or chronic transplant rejection or T-cell mediated inflammatory or autoimmune diseases, e.g. as indicated above, in a subject in need of such treatment, which method comprises administering to said subject an effective amount of a compound of formula I or a pharmaceutically acceptable salt thereof;
2. A compound of formula I, in free form or in a pharmaceutically acceptable salt form for use as a pharmaceutical, e.g. in any of the methods as indicated under 1.1 and 1.2 above.
3. A pharmaceutical composition, e.g. for use in any of the methods as in 1.1 and 1.2 above comprising a compound of formula I in free form or pharmaceutically acceptable salt form in association with a pharmaceutically acceptable diluent or carrier therefor.
4. A compound of formula I or a pharmaceutically acceptable salt thereof for use in the preparation of a pharmaceutical composition for use in any of the method as in 1.1 and 1.2 above.

claim.claim-text:
Verbindung nach Anspruch 1, ausgewählt aus
3-(1H-Indol-3-yl)-4-[5-(4-methylpiperazin-1-yl)-2-nitrophenyl]pyrrol-2,5-dion;
3-(7-Methyl-1H-indol-3-yl)-4-[5-(4-methylpiperazin-1-yl)-2-nitrophenyl]pyrrol-2,5-dion;
3-[2-Fluor-5-(4-methylpiperazin-1-yl)phenyl]-4-(1H-indol-3-yl)pyrrol-2,5-dion;
3-[2-Fluor-5-(4-methylpiperazin-1-yl)phenyl]-4-(1-methyl-1H-indol-3-yl)pyrrol-2,5-dion;
3-[2-Fluor-5-(4-methylpiperazin-1-yl)phenyl]-4-(7-methyl-1H-indol-3-yl)pyrrol-2,5-dion;
3-[2,4-Difluor-5-(4-methylpiperazin-1-yl)phenyl]-4-(1H-indol-3-yl)pyrrol-2,5-dion; und
3-[2,4-Difluor-5-(4-methylpiperazin-1-yl) phenyl]-4-(1-methyl-1H-indol-3-yl)pyrrol-2,5-dion.

A compound of formula I

wherein
Ra is H or methyl;
Rb is H, methyl or ethyl; and
R is a radical of formula (a)

wherein R1 is methyl and R2, independently, is H or methyl;
R3 is F or nitro, and R3 is attached in position 2; and
R4 is H or F and is attached in position 4;
or a salt thereof.

A compound according to claim 1 which is selected from
3-(1H-Indol-3-yl)-4-[5-(4-methyl-piperazin-1-yl)-2-nitro-phenyl]-pyrrole-2,5-dione;
3-(7-Methyl-1H-indol-3-yl)-4-[5-(4-methyl-piperazin-1-yl)-2-nitro-phenyl]-pyrrole-2,5-dione;
3-[2-Fluoro-5-(4-methyl-piperazin-1-yl)-phenyl]-4-(1H-indol-3-yl)-pyrrole-2,5-dione;
3-[2-Fluoro-5-(4-methyl-piperazin-1-yl)-phenyl]-4-(1-methyl-1H-indol-3-yl)-pyrrole-2,5-dione;
3-[2-Fluoro-5-(4-methyl-piperazin-1-yl)-phenyl]-4-(7-methyl-1H-indol-3-yl)-pyrrole-2,5-dione;
3-[2,4-Difluoro-5-(4-methyl-piperazin-1-yl)-phenyl]-4-(1H-indol-3-yl)-pyrrole-2,5-dione; and
3-[2,4-Difluoro-5-(4-methyl-piperazin-1-yl)-phenyl]-4-(1-methyl-1H-indol-3-yl)-pyrrole-2,5-dione.

Composé de formule I

où
Ra représente H ou un groupement méthyle ;
Rb représente H ou un groupement méthyle ou éthyle ; et
R représente un radical de formule (a)

où R1 représente un groupement méthyle et R2 représente indépendamment H ou un groupement méthyle ;
R3 représente F ou un groupement nitro, et R3 est attaché à la position 2 ;

et
R4 représente H ou F et est attaché à la position 4 ;
ou l'un de ses sels.

Composé conforme à la revendication 1, sélectionné parmi les suivantes :
